snippet.title: GO-GO Grapple Staff project announcement
snippet.description:
Nob Media gets interrupted by a mysterious Wizard wielding the power of the GRAPPLE STAFF! 

This marks the beginning of our first big game project! We'll continue to bring you updates and content in the following months, make sure to subscribe and share with your friends otherwise the Wizard may come for you! 

This video is a part of a much larger one! Make sure to check it out below:
https://youtu.be/DAzQyoexTYA?si=aRYd8YI5W5pGeyxz

:0 :▷
